headline: Buy 5 Old Economy Stocks Post Solid Earnings in Last Reported Quarter
summary: PH, GS, GE, CHRW and CRS are five old-economy stocks that posted strong quarterly earnings, signaling potential upside in 2026.

headline: Tariff bills across U.S. states mount as affordability and Trump head for midterm elections showdown
summary: New data shows that states where key midterm elections races will take place paid over $134 billion in tariffs during 2025 as affordability issues mounted.
